timing_disabl..._gating_checks(25.10)    timing_disabl..._gating_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_inferred_clock_gating_checks

Syntax
       timing_disable_inferred_clock_gating_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: false (performs checks)

       When  set  to  true,  disables clock gating checks that are inferred on
       combinational elements in the clock path. Explicit clock gating  checks
       that  are  described  in  the  timing  library are not affected by this
       global variable.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

